20via%20%3Ccode%3E%2B0x40%3C%2Fcode%3E.%20In%20digit%20mode%2C%20%3Ccode%3E%2B0x20%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20so%20the%20same%20value%20%3Ccode%3E0x12%3C%2Fcode%3E%20produces%20%3Ccode%3ER%3C%2Fcode%3E%20in%20letter%20mode%20and%20%3Ccode%3E2%3C%2Fcode%3E%20in%20digit%20mode.%20A%20%3Ccode%3E0x1E%3C%2Fcode%3E%20byte%20toggles%20between%20them.%20This%20lets%20numbers%20and%20punctuation%20share%20the%20same%205-bit%20value%20space%20as%20letters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20id%3D%22why-the-ratios-varied%22%3EWhy%20the%20Ratios%20Varied%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20variable%20bits-per-character%20ratio%20that%20initially%20confused%20us%20comes%20from%20three%20sources%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMode%20toggles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Every%20digit%2C%20quote%2C%20or%20comma%20costs%20an%20extra%200x1E%20byte.%20%E2%80%9C1984%E2%80%9D%20needs%20a%20toggle%20in%2C%20four%20digits%2C%20and%20a%20toggle%20out%2C%206%20values%20for%204%20displayed%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20separator%20flag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Field%20separators%20(between%20question%20and%20answers)%20consume%20zero%20data%20bits%20when%20they%20align%20with%20the%20flag%20bit.%20A%20word%20that%20happens%20to%20be%20the%20last%20in%20a%20field%20gets%20its%20flag%20set%20for%20free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShort%20answers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CFIVE%E2%80%9D%20is%204%20characters%20%2B%20separator%20%3D%205%20values%20in%20~4%20bytes.%20%E2%80%9CAUSTRALIAN%20FOOTBALL%E2%80%9D%20is%2019%20characters%20in%20~13%20bytes.%20The%20overhead%20is%20amortized%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch3%20id%3D%22the-content%22%3EThe%20Content%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E50%2C816%20questions%20across%2060%2B%20category%20chips%20spanning%20Series%208%20through%2018%0Aplus%20the%20compilation%20and%20gt103%20variant%20packs%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cpre%20tabindex%3D%220%22%3E%3Ccode%3E%20%20Series%208%3A%20%20%20%202%2C666%20questions%20%20(Science%2C%20General%2C%20S